# Centralized Farming Solutions Platform

## Overview
This document outlines the features and components of a centralized website/application designed to address various needs and challenges faced by farmers. The platform integrates multiple functionalities to support farmers in managing their crops, irrigation, disease prevention, and more.

## Features

### 1. Government Schemes
- **Description:** A comprehensive list of all government schemes available for farmers.
- **Functionality:** Links to official government pages providing detailed information about each scheme.

### 2. Crop and Farming Database
- **Description:** A detailed database encompassing information on crops, farming methods, diseases, and seasonal practices.
- **Content:** Includes general descriptions and guidelines for each category.

### 3. Irrigation Notifications
- **Description:** Automated notifications for irrigation based on crop requirements and weather conditions.
- **Functionality:** Provides timely reminders for optimal irrigation.

### 4. Multi-Language API-Based Chatbot
- **Description:** A simple chatbot capable of processing both written and voice inputs in multiple languages.
- **API:** Google API for translation.
- **Status:** Currently non-functional due to exhaustion of free quota for ChatGPT API.

### 5. Language Support
- **Description:** Ability to change the website language for improved communication and understanding.
- **Functionality:** Enhanced user experience through multilingual support.

### 6. Soil Prediction Model
- **Description:** A Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) based model for recommending crops based on soil conditions.
- **Accuracy:** 97%
- **Dataset Used:** [Soil Image Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/jayaprakashpondy/soil-image-dataset)

### 7. Real-Time Weather Access
- **Description:** Integration with Arduino sensors to provide real-time data on soil moisture, temperature, and humidity.
- **Sensors:** Connected to soil and temperature sensors.
- **API:** Weather API for surrounding temperature and humidity data.

### 8. Plant Disease Prediction Model
- **Description:** A CNN-based model for predicting plant diseases with recommendations for prevention and treatment.
- **Accuracy:** 98%
- **Dataset Used:** [New Plant Diseases Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/vipoooool/new-plant-diseases-dataset)

### 9. Minimum Support Price (MSP) Rates
- **Description:** Up-to-date information on MSP rates for various crops.
- **Functionality:** Provides current rates to aid farmers in financial planning.

### 10. Supply Chain Management
- **Description:** Notifications about government tenders for crop procurement.
- **Functionality:** Alerts farmers to tender releases and procurement opportunities.

### 11. Crop Insurance Schemes
- **Description:** Links to crop insurance schemes offered by the government.
- **Functionality:** Provides information on available insurance options.

## Technical Implementation

### Data Sources
- **Soil Dataset:** [Kaggle Soil Image Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/jayaprakashpondy/soil-image-dataset)
- **Plant Diseases Dataset:** [Kaggle New Plant Diseases Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/vipoooool/new-plant-diseases-dataset)
- **Database Creation:** Database of crop data created using prompt engineering techniques.

### APIs and Tools
- **Translation API:** Google API for language translation.
- **Weather API:** Used for real-time temperature and humidity data.
- **ChatGPT API:** Required for chatbot responses (currently non-functional).

### Model Information
- **Soil Prediction Model:** Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) with 97% accuracy.
- **Plant Disease Prediction Model:** Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) with 98% accuracy.
- **Model Weight Files:** Provided for both CNN models.

## Notes
- All datasets and models were used for demonstration purposes.
- The chatbot functionality is currently limited due to API quota restrictions.
